Paper: hep-th/9603027

Date: 1996-03-06

Title: Gravitating BPS Dyons witout a Dilaton

Authors: Choonkyu Lee, Q-Han Park

Comments: 10 pages

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B387 (1996) 478-482

We describe curved-space BPS dyon solutions, the ADM mass of which saturatesthe gravitational version of the Bogomol'nyi bound. This generalizesself-gravitating BPS monopole solutions of Gibbons et al. when there is nodilaton.